S.FORM: = Hans-Adam II = Mntucing hngkawas 1945 idas 2 jiyax 14 ka Hans-Adam II ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bukung klwaan Liechtenstein ta sayang o kiya ka Hans-Adam II, pnaah hngkawas 1989 idas 11 jiyax 13 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan. Hans Adam II Cinwang Bukung (Hans-Adam II, kana hangan: Johannes "Hans" Adam Ferdinand Aloys Josef Maria Marko d'Aviano Pius; hangan seyhu: Hans Adam II von and zu Liechtenstein, hangan hniwan: HSH The Prince of Liechtenstein, knkana hangan hnyuwan: splawa Fürst von und zu Liechtenstein, Duke von Troppau und Jägerndorf, Count zu Rietberg, kngkawas 1945 idas 2 diyax 14－), Tukcka O Co qnlhangan Liechtenstein weynso, kiya ka laqi qbsuran Franz Joseph II (kngkawas 1906-1989) mi tuhuy qridin niya Georgiana Wilczek. Hans Adam II pa mntuting Switzerland Zurich, laqi cida daw wada phyuwan mpBukung, kiya ka Wangs sediq mpqlahang jaysang niya. Kngkawas 1984 idas 8 prading rmirih tama niya Josef II qmlahang qnlhangan. Kngkawas 1989 idas 11 diyax 13 cida wada mrdang ka Josef II, mntna diyax, Hans Adam II ka pusa kari rm irih mBukung, hangan pnsdhuwan ka Hans Adam II. Nasi ini spuwi ka Cyawcong pa, Hans Adam II ka Oco murux mndungus bay niqan biyax niya Cyuncu, kiya ka mnnniqan balay snbliqan dmuwi Cyuncu. Kngkawas 2003 muda mntxan kongto, muda psdhu ya muda pkrana biyax niya. Hans Adam II u muda psicu nasi ini pnlngu lnglungan niya ka ndanan daw, musa thdil nganguc Liechtenstein, kiya mi musa mniq Austria. Kiya u wada mdhu balay pkrana ka biyax niya Hans Adam II. Kngkawas 2012 quri so ya klihun ka biyax Cinwang na kongto pa wada hbaraw balay ka ini sruwa uri. Llaqi niya 子嗣 Hans Adam II tuhuy Cinwanghuy qridin niya Marie Aglaë, Countess Kinsky von Wchinitz und Tettau mniq kngkawas 1967 idas 7 diyax 30 wada msturung mi msdungus, niqan 4 laqi dha: · Alois mpBukung, kngkawas 1968 idas 6 diyax 11 mntuting Switzerland Zurich, kngkawas 2004 cida alaw Hans Adam II iyux mpmalax Bukung mi mpSecng; qridin niya ka Pakriya na Sohuy kongcu (kngkawas 1967 idas 10 diyax 28 mntuting Doicu Munich) ddha dha u mniq kngkawas 1993 idas 7 diyax 3 mniq Vaduz msturung. · Maximilian Nikolaus Maria Wangc, kngkawas 1969 idas 5 diyax 16 mntuting Switzerland St Gallen, qridin niya ka Angela Gisele Brown (kngkawas 1958 idas 2 diyax 3 mntuting Panama Bocas del Toro), ddha dha u mniq kngkawas 2000 idas 1 msturung. · Constantin Ferdinand Maria Wangc, kngkawas 1972 idas 3 diyax 15 mntuting Switzerland St Gallen, qridin niya ka Marie Gabriele Franciska Countess Kálnoky de Köröspatak (kngkawas 1975 idas 7 diyax 16 mntuting Austria Graz), ddha dha u mniq kngkawas 1999 idas 7 msturung. · Tatjana Nora Maria Kongcu, kngkawas 1973 idas 4 diyax 10 mntuting Switzerland St. Gallen, snaw niya ka Philipp von Lattorf, kngkawas 1968 idas 3 diyax 25 tntuting Austria Graz, ddha dha u mniq kngkawas 1999 idas 6 diyax 5 msturung.

= Hans-Adam II = Mntocing hngkawas 1945 idas 2 jiyax 14 ka Hans-Adam II ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bokong klwaan Liechtenstein ta sayang o kiya ka Hans-Adam II, pnaah hngkawas 1989 idas 11 jiyax 13 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan. Hans Adam II Cinwang Bokong (Hans-Adam II, kana hangan: Johannes "Hans" Adam Ferdinand Aloys Josef Maria Marko d'Aviano Pios; hangan seyho: Hans Adam II von and zo Liechtenstein, hangan hniwan: HSH The Prince of Liechtenstein, knkana hangan hnyowan: splawa Fürst von ond zo Liechtenstein, Doke von Troppao ond Jägerndorf, Coont zo Rietberg, kngkawas 1945 idas 2 diyax 14－), Tokcka O Co qnlhangan Liechtenstein weynso, kiya ka laqi qbsoran Franz Joseph II (kngkawas 1906-1989) mi tohoy qridin niya Georgiana Wilczek. Hans Adam II pa mntoting Switzerland Zorich, laqi cida daw wada phyowan mpBokong, kiya ka Wangs sediq mpqlahang jaysang niya. Kngkawas 1984 idas 8 prading rmirih tama niya Josef II qmlahang qnlhangan. Kngkawas 1989 idas 11 diyax 13 cida wada mrdang ka Josef II, mntna diyax, Hans Adam II ka posa kari rm irih mBokong, hangan pnsdhowan ka Hans Adam II. Nasi ini spowi ka Cyawcong pa, Hans Adam II ka Oco morox mndongos bay niqan biyax niya Cyonco, kiya ka mnnniqan balay snbliqan dmowi Cyonco. Kngkawas 2003 moda mntxan kongto, moda psdho ya moda pkrana biyax niya. Hans Adam II o moda psico nasi ini pnlngo lnglongan niya ka ndanan daw, mosa thdil ngangoc Liechtenstein, kiya mi mosa mniq Aostria. Kiya o wada mdho balay pkrana ka biyax niya Hans Adam II. Kngkawas 2012 qori so ya klihon ka biyax Cinwang na kongto pa wada hbaraw balay ka ini srowa ori. Llaqi niya 子嗣 Hans Adam II tohoy Cinwanghoy qridin niya Marie Aglaë, Coontess Kinsky von Wchinitz ond Tettao mniq kngkawas 1967 idas 7 diyax 30 wada mstorong mi msdongos, niqan 4 laqi dha: · Alois mpBokong, kngkawas 1968 idas 6 diyax 11 mntoting Switzerland Zorich, kngkawas 2004 cida alaw Hans Adam II iyox mpmalax Bokong mi mpSecng; qridin niya ka Pakriya na Sohoy kongco (kngkawas 1967 idas 10 diyax 28 mntoting Doico Monich) ddha dha o mniq kngkawas 1993 idas 7 diyax 3 mniq Vadoz mstorong. · Maximilian Nikolaos Maria Wangc, kngkawas 1969 idas 5 diyax 16 mntoting Switzerland St Gallen, qridin niya ka Angela Gisele Brown (kngkawas 1958 idas 2 diyax 3 mntoting Panama Bocas del Toro), ddha dha o mniq kngkawas 2000 idas 1 mstorong. · Constantin Ferdinand Maria Wangc, kngkawas 1972 idas 3 diyax 15 mntoting Switzerland St Gallen, qridin niya ka Marie Gabriele Franciska Coontess Kálnoky de Köröspatak (kngkawas 1975 idas 7 diyax 16 mntoting Aostria Graz), ddha dha o mniq kngkawas 1999 idas 7 mstorong. · Tatjana Nora Maria Kongco, kngkawas 1973 idas 4 diyax 10 mntoting Switzerland St. Gallen, snaw niya ka Philipp von Lattorf, kngkawas 1968 idas 3 diyax 25 tntoting Aostria Graz, ddha dha o mniq kngkawas 1999 idas 6 diyax 5 mstorong.
